data.title: Duck Soup
data.meta_description: Duck Soup (1933) starring Groucho Marx, Harpo Marx, Chico Marx and directed by Leo McCarey.
data.text: Rufus T. Firefly is named the dictator of bankrupt Freedonia and declares war on neighboring Sylvania over the love of his wealthy backer Mrs. Teasdale, contending with two inept spies who can't seem to keep straight which side they're on.
